name: Senior #28 - Li Li
description:
Li Li is a 66-year-old high-end fashion magazine Editor-in-chief who enjoys working tirelessly, eating zero-calorie meals, and throwing things to her staff. She is extremely driven and sharp, but can also be very brutal and unkind.

She is a divorcée who defines herself as asexual. Her most recent romance was with a rich heir named Giotto. They broke up after Li Li accidentally found a pair of crocs sandals in Giotto’s closet.
